------------------ Homepage: www.woomaps.pl/main Server: 88.151.144.73:27015 ------------------ Woo proudly presents.... De_bridgev8! This map features:

-Destructable train!

-Preformance Enhancements -Deadly train -Camping towers -Destructable towers and buildings -Balanced gameplay -And much more! T's can jump onto the train and take the fast route to the CT side to plant to bomb, or just walk on the walkay under the bridge! Watch out for snipers in the two ct towers! Dont worry if you get there though, because you can show those campers whos who by blowing their tower up, and send them plummeting into the canyon! Check out some more of my maps on our server!
